wAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=Moin,+Khomeini,+2001#v=onepage&q&f=false |ref=harv |language=en}}\n* {{cite journal |ref=harv |first=James A. |last=Piazza |title = The Democratic Islamic Republic of Iran in Exile |date=October 1994 |journal = Digest of Middle East Studies |volume=3 |issue=4 |pages = 9\u201343 |doi=10.1111/j.1949-3606.1994.tb00535.x}}\n* {{cite book |ref=harv |first=Sepehr |last=Zabih |chapter = The Non-Communist Left in Iran: The Case of the Mujahidin |pages = 241\u2013258 |title = Ideology and Power in the Middle East |editor-first1=Peter J. |editor-last1=Chelkowski |editor-first2=Robert J. |editor-last2=Pranger |year=1988 |publisher = Duke University Press |isbn = 978-0-8223-8150-1}}\n{{refend}}\n\n== External links ==\n{{Commons category}}\n{{Wikiquote}}\n* {{official website |url = https://www.mojahedin.org/home/en}}\n\n{{Iranian exiled parties|state=collapsed}}\n{{Iran\u2013Iraq War|state=collapsed}}\n{{Iran\u2013United States relations}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:People's Mojahedin of Iran}}\n[[Category:People's Mujahedin of Iran| ]]\n[[Category:1965 establishments in Iran]]\n[[Category:Banned political parties in Iran]]\n[[Category:Banned socialist parties]]\n[[Category:Cults of personality]]\n[[Category:Entities added to the Consolidated List by Australia]]\n[[Category:Foreign relations during the Iran\u2013Iraq War]]\n[[Category:France\u2013Iran relations]]\n[[Category:Guerrilla organizations]]\n[[Category:Iran\u2013Iraq relations]]\n[[Category:Iran\u2013Israel relations]]\n[[Category:Iran\u2013Saudi Arabia relations]]\n[[Category:Iran\u2013Soviet Union relations]]\n[[Category:Iran\u2013United States relations]]\n[[Category:Iranian fraudsters]]\n[[Category:Iranian money launderers]]\n[[Category:Iranian nationalism]]\n[[Category:Islamic political parties in Iran]]\n[[Category:Islamic socialism]]\n[[Category:Islamist groups]]\n[[Category:Left-wing militant groups in Iran]]\n[[Category:Left-wing nationalist parties]]\n[[Category:Left-wing populism]]\n[[