{"title_page": "Opalchenska Metro Station", "text_new": "{{Short description|S\u043efia metro station}}\n{{Infobox station\n| name                = [[File:Sofia Metro Logo.svg|27px|link=Sofia Metro]] Opalchenska\n| style               = Sofia Metro\n| image               = Opalchenska Metrostation.jpg\n| coordinates         = {{coord|42|42|00|N|23|18|36|E|display=inline,title}}\n| owned               = [[Sofia#Administration|Sofia Municipality]]\n| structure           = sub-surface\n| platform            = island\n| levels              = 2\n| tracks              = 2\n| code                = 3011; 3012\n| opened              = {{Start date|1999|09|17|df=y}}\n| services            = {{s-rail|title=Sofia Metro}}\n{{s-line|system=Sofia Metro|line=Line 1|previous=Konstantin Velichkov|next=Serdika}}\n{{s-line|system=Sofia Metro|line=Line 2|previous=Konstantin Velichkov|next=Serdika}}\n| map_locator         = [[File:Map8 eng trans.png|300px]]\n}}\n{{Sofia Metro Red line}}\n{{Sofia Metro Blue line}}\n'''Opalchenska Metro Station''' ({{lang-bg|\u041c\u0435\u0442\u0440\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u0446\u0438\u044f \u201e\u041e\u043f\u044a\u043b\u0447\u0435\u043d\u0441\u043a\u0430\u201c}}) is a station on the [[Sofia Metro]] in [[Bulgaria]].  It started operation on September 17, 1999.\n\n==Public Transportation==\n* [[Sofia Tramway|Tramway service]]: 3, 8, 10, 20, 22\n* [[Trolleybuses in Sofia|Trolleybus service]]: 1, 5\n* [[Public buses in Sofia|City Bus service]]: 60, 74\n\n==Location==\n{{Empty section|date=October 2012}}\n\n==Gallery==\n{{Empty section|date=February 2015}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commonscat-inline|Opalchenska (Sofia Metro)|Opalchenska Metro Station}}\n* [http://metropolitan.bg/panoramas/5.htm 360 degrees panorama from inside the station]\n* [http://www.metropolitan.bg/ Sofia Metropolitan (Official site)]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20090826175543/http://metropolitan.hit.bg/ Unofficial site]\n* [http://www.360.bg/index.php?lat=42.699723&lon=23.31024